name: Pixel Fish!
description:
Pixel Fish is a fun fish eater game with original Pixel art! It is basically the pixelated version of my other fish game!

Swim through the infinite ocean, eat grow and then eat more, until noone stands in your way!

A high score system is included!
It's an online browser game, completely free!

The original artwork was created by PxlSyl!
Check out more of his art here:
PxlSyl's art

Enjoy!
